DATA & NETWORK DISCLOSURE:
This mod is client-side only and makes outbound network requests solely when
you choose to use its upload or sharing features. Specifically:

- When you upload a screenshot using the screenshot.rest provider, the image
  is transmitted to and stored on screenshot.rest, a service operated by rzr.
  Uploaded images are publicly accessible via their direct URL.
- When any upload or clipboard copy action completes, the mod sends an
  anonymous usage count (provider name only, no image data, no personal
  information) to screenshot.rest for aggregate statistics displayed on
  quicksnap.pics. No identifying information is collected or stored.
- When using third-party providers (Litterbox, Imgur, or a custom endpoint),
  your image is sent directly to that provider and is subject to their own
  terms of service. rzr has no control over third-party providers.
- The mod does not collect usernames, UUIDs, IP addresses, or any personally
  identifiable information.

